# Bento Grid Verification Checklist
- [ ] Navigate to http://localhost:3000/vi
- [ ] Find the Bento Grid section
- [ ] Hover over the left tall Bento box and verify:
    - [ ] Light covers full height
    - [ ] Light is centered on border line
    - [ ] Curvature matches box exactly
- [ ] Hover over the top right smaller Bento box and verify:
    - [ ] Light covers full height
    - [ ] Light is centered on border line
    - [ ] Curvature matches box exactly
- [ ] Hover over the bottom right smaller Bento box and verify:
    - [ ] Light covers full height
    - [ ] Light is centered on border line
    - [ ] Curvature matches box exactly
- [ ] Capture screenshot of the section with one box hovered
- [ ] Report results